Sentencas: This work is among the first where the results of an extensive experimental research programme are compared to performance calculations of a comprehensive computational fluid dynamics model for a solid oxide fuel cell stack.
Titulo: Three-dimensional computational fluid dynamics modelling and experimental validation of the Julich Mark-F solid oxide fuel cell stack

Sentencas: The model, which combines electrochemical reactions with momentum, heat, and mass transport, is used to obtain results for an established industrial-scale fuel cell stack design with complex manifolds.
Titulo: Three-dimensional computational fluid dynamics modelling and experimental validation of the Julich Mark-F solid oxide fuel cell stack

Sentencas: To validate the model, comparisons with experimentally gathered voltage and temperature data are made for the Julich Mark-F, 18-cell stack operating in a test furnace.
Titulo: Three-dimensional computational fluid dynamics modelling and experimental validation of the Julich Mark-F solid oxide fuel cell stack

Sentencas: Good agreement is obtained between the model and experiment results for cell voltages and temperature distributions, confirming the validity of the computational methodology for stack design.
Titulo: Three-dimensional computational fluid dynamics modelling and experimental validation of the Julich Mark-F solid oxide fuel cell stack

Sentencas: The transient effects during ramp up of current in the experiment may explain a lower average voltage than model predictions for the power curve.
Titulo: Three-dimensional computational fluid dynamics modelling and experimental validation of the Julich Mark-F solid oxide fuel cell stack
